<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q37_v3" title="Q37_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      En un juego, la puntuación <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math> que obtiene un equipo se calcula mediante la expresión
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
      </m:math>,
      donde <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> es el número de tiros acertados.
      Si un equipo obtuvo
      <m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math>
      puntos de puntuación, ¿cuántos tiros acertó ese equipo?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac><m:mn>38</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>38</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, entonces al reemplazar en la expresión se obtiene <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>38</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>38</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:math>. Por lo tanto, esa opción no produce <m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math> puntos.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el equipo acertó 8 tiros.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>34</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>198</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="FB_NoResponse" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p>No se seleccionó una alternativa válida. Para resolver el problema, se reemplaza <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math> en <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
        <p><m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math></p>
        <p>Luego, se suma <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math> a ambos lados:</p>
        <p><m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math></p>
        <p>Finalmente, se divide por <m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
        <p><m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math></p>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Reemplazar la puntuación conocida en la expresión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión dada es <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>. Como el equipo obtuvo <m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math> puntos, se reemplaza <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math> por <m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Despejar <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math></strong></p>
            <p>Se suma <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math> en ambos lados:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>38</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Dividir entre 5</strong></p>
            <p>Ahora se divide ambos lados por <m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar la respuesta</strong></p>
            <p>Se reemplaza <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> en la expresión original:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>38</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El equipo acertó <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> tiros. La alternativa correcta es la B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_NoResponse</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>